headline: November Home Sales Post Biggest Annual Gain Since 2021
summary: Sales of existing homes rose in November, notching the biggest year-over-year gain in more than three years.

headline: Government Contractor KBR, Recently Hit by DOGE Fears, Draws Activist Investor
summary: Irenic Capital Management has built a stake in KBR and plans to push the company to separate its segment that serves the private sector.
